snippet.textDisplay: Wow! It's pure magic from 03:40 onward, Suchi's swarams and Blaaze's rap - such a beautiful marriage of two different styles. And I really had goosebumps with patriotism at few places in 2nd half, one of ARR's best work ever! And such great backing vocals, very difficult classic chorus portion, and they did so well. At some point, all the musicians forgot it was studio & they were making music and gave themselves in to the magic of the moment! Kudos!
snippet.textOriginal: Wow! It's pure magic from 03:40 onward, Suchi's swarams and Blaaze's rap - such a beautiful marriage of two different styles. And I really had goosebumps with patriotism at few places in 2nd half, one of ARR's best work ever! And such great backing vocals, very difficult classic chorus portion, and they did so well.
